'Can do I do Internet/WWW programming with Prolog:'

Prolog is very suitable for this task. Several commercial and free
implementations include special support for it. A page specifically on
this topic (including some tutorials) is maintained at
http://www.clip.dia.fi.upm.es/lpnet/lpnet.html 
A public-domain library exists (PiLLoW) for several popular Prolog
systems which helps in the task. See:
http://www.clip.dia.fi.upm.es/Software/pillow

